  "body": "### Version of Hardhat\n\n2.16.1\n\n### What happened?\n\nWhile trying to compile a contract in a hardhat project, I received this error. I see that this issue has been raised before but is closed as resolved. It appears to be tracked on Linear but it seems outside users don't have access to this workspace. \n\n### Minimal reproduction steps\n\nError HH1006: The file /Users/coopermaira/Documents/GitHub/ethernaut-master/attempt1/node_modules/eth-gas-reporter/mock/contracts/ConvertLib.sol is treated as local but is inside a node_modules directory\r\n\r\nHardhatError: HH1006: The file /Users/coopermaira/Documents/GitHub/ethernaut-master/attempt1/node_modules/eth-gas-reporter/mock/contracts/ConvertLib.sol is treated as local but is inside a node_modules directory\r\n    at localPathToSourceName (/Users/coopermaira/Documents/GitHub/ethernaut-master/attempt1/node_modules/hardhat/src/utils/source-names.ts:132:11)\r\n    at /Users/coopermaira/Documents/GitHub/ethernaut-master/attempt1/node_modules/hardhat/src/builtin-tasks/compile.ts:154:32\r\n    at Array.map (<anonymous>)\r\n    at SimpleTaskDefinition.action (/Users/coopermaira/Documents/GitHub/ethernaut-master/attempt1/node_modules/hardhat/src/builtin-tasks/compile.ts:153:21)\r\n    at Environment._runTaskDefinition (/Users/coopermaira/Documents/GitHub/ethernaut-master/attempt1/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/core/runtime-environment.ts:333:35)\r\n    at Environment.run (/Users/coopermaira/Documents/GitHub/ethernaut-master/attempt1/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/core/runtime-environment.ts:166:25)\r\n    at /Users/coopermaira/Documents/GitHub/ethernaut-master/attempt1/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/core/runtime-environment.ts:292:29\r\n    at SimpleTaskDefinition.action (/Users/coopermaira/Documents/GitHub/ethernaut-master/attempt1/node_modules/hardhat/src/builtin-tasks/compile.ts:1304:43)\r\n    at async Environment._runTaskDefinition (/Users/coopermaira/Documents/GitHub/ethernaut-master/attempt1/nod